# -- NOTE: The following URLs exist in classes4.dex which cannot be safely
# patched (baksmali/smali round-trip causes IncompatibleClassChangeError,
# and binary string replacement breaks DEX string table sort order).
# They remain active but have limited impact:
#   - https://clientservices.googleapis.com/chrome-variations/seed (A/B testing)
#   - https://permanently-removed.invalid/cr/report (already invalid domain)
#   - https://prod.rewardsplatform.microsoft.com/dapi/me/activities/ (rewards API)
#   - https://api.webxtsvc.microsoft.com (web extensions telemetry)
